{"pageProps":{"post":{"id":"wpxml-y-proofreading","title":"Gutenberg用の校正プラグインを作成しました","content":"<html><head></head><body><div class=\"toc-wrapper\"><input type=\"checkbox\" class=\"toc-checkbox\" id=\"toc-checkbox-d8bhd802du\" checked><label class=\"toc-title\" for=\"toc-checkbox-d8bhd802du\">目次</label><nav class=\"toc\"><ol class=\"toc-level toc-level-1\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h2\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h2\" href=\"#機能\">機能</a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h2\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h2\" href=\"#導入手順\">導入手順</a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h2\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h2\" href=\"#使用方法\">使用方法</a><ol class=\"toc-level toc-level-2\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h3\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h3\" href=\"#校正機能の使用\">校正機能の使用</a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h3\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h3\" href=\"#結果の表示\">結果の表示</a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h3\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h3\" href=\"#指摘事項の一覧表示\">指摘事項の一覧表示</a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h3\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h3\" href=\"#再度実行\">再度実行</a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h3\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h3\" href=\"#サイズ設定\">サイズ設定</a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h3\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h3\" href=\"#プラグインの再固定\">プラグインの再固定</a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h2\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h2\" href=\"#設定\">設定</a><ol class=\"toc-level toc-level-2\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h3\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h3\" href=\"#yahooapi-の-client-id\">Yahoo!API の Client ID</a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h3\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h3\" href=\"#除外する指摘\">除外する指摘</a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h2\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h2\" href=\"#yahooapi-校正支援\">Yahoo!API 校正支援</a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h2\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h2\" href=\"#利用制限\">利用制限</a><ol class=\"toc-level toc-level-2\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h3\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h3\" href=\"#1リクエストあたりの制限\">1リクエストあたりの制限</a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h3\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h3\" href=\"#24時間以内のリクエスト数制限\">24時間以内のリクエスト数制限</a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h2\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h2\" href=\"#要件\">要件</a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h2\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h2\" href=\"#要望バグ報告等\">要望・バグ報告等</a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h2\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h2\" href=\"#今後の予定等\">今後の予定等</a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-item-h2\"><a class=\"toc-link toc-link-h2\" href=\"#使用しているフレームワーク\">使用しているフレームワーク</a></li></ol></nav></div><figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https://technote.space/uploads/2019/04/04101545.gif\"><img src=\"https://technote.space/uploads/2019/04/04101545.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1426\"></a></figure>\n\n<div class=\"blog-card\"><iframe src=\"https://blog-card-ten.vercel.app/card/https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Ftechnote-space%2Fy-proofreading?id=blog-card-q9scn8ee4f&#x26;referrer=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnote.space%2Fposts%2Fwpxml-y-proofreading%2F\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" loading=\"lazy\" data-id=\"blog-card-q9scn8ee4f\"></iframe></div>\n\n<h2 id=\"機能\">機能<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#機能\"><svg class=\"icon icon-link\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-labelledby=\"paperclipIconTitle\" stroke=\"#2329EE\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-linejoin=\"miter\" fill=\"none\" color=\"#131996\"><path d=\"M7.93517339,13.7795989 L15.1617306,6.55304173 C16.03921,5.67631227 17.4656766,5.67631227 18.343156,6.55304173 C19.2206355,7.43052116 19.2206355,8.85773771 18.343156,9.73521714 L8.40091248,19.5477137 C6.93619681,21.0124294 4.56325242,21.0124294 3.09853675,19.5477137 C1.63382108,18.083748 1.63382108,15.7093037 3.09853675,14.245338 L12.9335328,4.53783896 C14.9839848,2.48738701 18.3094068,2.48738701 20.3568588,4.53783896 C22.4088107,6.58904088 22.4088107,9.91146301 20.3583588,11.961915 L13.2390491,19.0819746\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n\n<p><em>Yahoo!API</em> の校正支援APIを利用して校正を行います。</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"導入手順\"><a href=\"https://github.com/technote-space/y-proofreading#%E5%B0%8E%E5%85%A5%E6%89%8B%E9%A0%86\"></a>導入手順<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#導入手順\"><svg class=\"icon icon-link\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-labelledby=\"paperclipIconTitle\" stroke=\"#2329EE\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-linejoin=\"miter\" fill=\"none\" color=\"#131996\"><path d=\"M7.93517339,13.7795989 L15.1617306,6.55304173 C16.03921,5.67631227 17.4656766,5.67631227 18.343156,6.55304173 C19.2206355,7.43052116 19.2206355,8.85773771 18.343156,9.73521714 L8.40091248,19.5477137 C6.93619681,21.0124294 4.56325242,21.0124294 3.09853675,19.5477137 C1.63382108,18.083748 1.63382108,15.7093037 3.09853675,14.245338 L12.9335328,4.53783896 C14.9839848,2.48738701 18.3094068,2.48738701 20.3568588,4.53783896 C22.4088107,6.58904088 22.4088107,9.91146301 20.3583588,11.961915 L13.2390491,19.0819746\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n\n<ol><li><a href=\"https://github.com/technote-space/y-proofreading/releases/latest/download/release.zip\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">ZIPをダウンロード</a></li><li>『プラグインのアップロード』からインストール<br><a href=\"https://technote.space/uploads/2019/01/04102143.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img class=\"wp-image-1428\" style=\"width: 150px;\" src=\"https://technote.space/uploads/2019/01/04102143.png\" alt=\"\"></a></li><li>プラグインを有効化</li><li><em>Yahoo! API</em> の <em>Client ID</em> を設定<ol><li><a href=\"https://developer.yahoo.co.jp/yconnect/v2/registration.html\">https://developer.yahoo.co.jp/yconnect/v2/registration.html</a><br>アプリケーションの種類は「サーバーサイド」</li><li>管理画面左メニュー『Y Proofreading』⇒『ダッシュボード』に移動</li><li>『Yahoo!API の Client ID』に取得した <em>アプリケーションID</em> を入力して『更新』ボタンを押下<br>(シークレットは使用しません)</li></ol></li></ol>\n\n<h2 id=\"使用方法\"><a href=\"https://github.com/technote-space/y-proofreading#%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95\"></a>使用方法<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#使用方法\"><svg class=\"icon icon-link\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-labelledby=\"paperclipIconTitle\" stroke=\"#2329EE\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-linejoin=\"miter\" fill=\"none\" color=\"#131996\"><path d=\"M7.93517339,13.7795989 L15.1617306,6.55304173 C16.03921,5.67631227 17.4656766,5.67631227 18.343156,6.55304173 C19.2206355,7.43052116 19.2206355,8.85773771 18.343156,9.73521714 L8.40091248,19.5477137 C6.93619681,21.0124294 4.56325242,21.0124294 3.09853675,19.5477137 C1.63382108,18.083748 1.63382108,15.7093037 3.09853675,14.245338 L12.9335328,4.53783896 C14.9839848,2.48738701 18.3094068,2.48738701 20.3568588,4.53783896 C22.4088107,6.58904088 22.4088107,9.91146301 20.3583588,11.961915 L13.2390491,19.0819746\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n\n<h3 id=\"校正機能の使用\"><a href=\"https://github.com/technote-space/y-proofreading#%E6%A0%A1%E6%AD%A3%E6%A9%9F%E8%83%BD%E3%81%AE%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8\"></a>校正機能の使用<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#校正機能の使用\"><svg class=\"icon icon-link\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-labelledby=\"paperclipIconTitle\" stroke=\"#2329EE\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-linejoin=\"miter\" fill=\"none\" color=\"#131996\"><path d=\"M7.93517339,13.7795989 L15.1617306,6.55304173 C16.03921,5.67631227 17.4656766,5.67631227 18.343156,6.55304173 C19.2206355,7.43052116 19.2206355,8.85773771 18.343156,9.73521714 L8.40091248,19.5477137 C6.93619681,21.0124294 4.56325242,21.0124294 3.09853675,19.5477137 C1.63382108,18.083748 1.63382108,15.7093037 3.09853675,14.245338 L12.9335328,4.53783896 C14.9839848,2.48738701 18.3094068,2.48738701 20.3568588,4.53783896 C22.4088107,6.58904088 22.4088107,9.91146301 20.3583588,11.961915 L13.2390491,19.0819746\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https://technote.space/uploads/2019/04/start-proofreading.png\"><img src=\"https://technote.space/uploads/2019/04/start-proofreading-256x300.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1432\"></a></figure>\n\n<p>サイドバーの「文書」タグの「校正」から実行します。</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"結果の表示\">結果の表示<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#結果の表示\"><svg class=\"icon icon-link\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-labelledby=\"paperclipIconTitle\" stroke=\"#2329EE\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-linejoin=\"miter\" fill=\"none\" color=\"#131996\"><path d=\"M7.93517339,13.7795989 L15.1617306,6.55304173 C16.03921,5.67631227 17.4656766,5.67631227 18.343156,6.55304173 C19.2206355,7.43052116 19.2206355,8.85773771 18.343156,9.73521714 L8.40091248,19.5477137 C6.93619681,21.0124294 4.56325242,21.0124294 3.09853675,19.5477137 C1.63382108,18.083748 1.63382108,15.7093037 3.09853675,14.245338 L12.9335328,4.53783896 C14.9839848,2.48738701 18.3094068,2.48738701 20.3568588,4.53783896 C22.4088107,6.58904088 22.4088107,9.91146301 20.3583588,11.961915 L13.2390491,19.0819746\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https://technote.space/uploads/2019/04/content-result.png\"><img src=\"https://technote.space/uploads/2019/04/content-result-239x300.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1433\"></a></figure>\n\n<p>結果はサイドバーに表示されます。<br>マウスでホバーすると指摘事項がポップアップで表示されます。</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"指摘事項の一覧表示\">指摘事項の一覧表示<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#指摘事項の一覧表示\"><svg class=\"icon icon-link\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-labelledby=\"paperclipIconTitle\" stroke=\"#2329EE\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-linejoin=\"miter\" fill=\"none\" color=\"#131996\"><path d=\"M7.93517339,13.7795989 L15.1617306,6.55304173 C16.03921,5.67631227 17.4656766,5.67631227 18.343156,6.55304173 C19.2206355,7.43052116 19.2206355,8.85773771 18.343156,9.73521714 L8.40091248,19.5477137 C6.93619681,21.0124294 4.56325242,21.0124294 3.09853675,19.5477137 C1.63382108,18.083748 1.63382108,15.7093037 3.09853675,14.245338 L12.9335328,4.53783896 C14.9839848,2.48738701 18.3094068,2.48738701 20.3568588,4.53783896 C22.4088107,6.58904088 22.4088107,9.91146301 20.3583588,11.961915 L13.2390491,19.0819746\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https://technote.space/uploads/2019/04/proofreading-info.png\"><img src=\"https://technote.space/uploads/2019/04/proofreading-info-221x300.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1434\"></a></figure>\n\n<p>『文章校正支援情報』タブから指摘の一覧を見ることが可能です。</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"再度実行\">再度実行<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#再度実行\"><svg class=\"icon icon-link\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-labelledby=\"paperclipIconTitle\" stroke=\"#2329EE\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-linejoin=\"miter\" fill=\"none\" color=\"#131996\"><path d=\"M7.93517339,13.7795989 L15.1617306,6.55304173 C16.03921,5.67631227 17.4656766,5.67631227 18.343156,6.55304173 C19.2206355,7.43052116 19.2206355,8.85773771 18.343156,9.73521714 L8.40091248,19.5477137 C6.93619681,21.0124294 4.56325242,21.0124294 3.09853675,19.5477137 C1.63382108,18.083748 1.63382108,15.7093037 3.09853675,14.245338 L12.9335328,4.53783896 C14.9839848,2.48738701 18.3094068,2.48738701 20.3568588,4.53783896 C22.4088107,6.58904088 22.4088107,9.91146301 20.3583588,11.961915 L13.2390491,19.0819746\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https://technote.space/uploads/2019/04/re-proofreading.png\"><img src=\"https://technote.space/uploads/2019/04/re-proofreading-300x133.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1435\"></a></figure>\n\n<p>『再度実行』から再度校正を行うことができます。</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"サイズ設定\">サイズ設定<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#サイズ設定\"><svg class=\"icon icon-link\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-labelledby=\"paperclipIconTitle\" stroke=\"#2329EE\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-linejoin=\"miter\" fill=\"none\" color=\"#131996\"><path d=\"M7.93517339,13.7795989 L15.1617306,6.55304173 C16.03921,5.67631227 17.4656766,5.67631227 18.343156,6.55304173 C19.2206355,7.43052116 19.2206355,8.85773771 18.343156,9.73521714 L8.40091248,19.5477137 C6.93619681,21.0124294 4.56325242,21.0124294 3.09853675,19.5477137 C1.63382108,18.083748 1.63382108,15.7093037 3.09853675,14.245338 L12.9335328,4.53783896 C14.9839848,2.48738701 18.3094068,2.48738701 20.3568588,4.53783896 C22.4088107,6.58904088 22.4088107,9.91146301 20.3583588,11.961915 L13.2390491,19.0819746\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"https://technote.space/uploads/2019/04/open-size-setting.png\"><img src=\"https://technote.space/uploads/2019/04/open-size-setting.png\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"1436\" data-link=\"/y-proofreading/attachment/open-size-setting\" class=\"wp-image-1436\"></a></figure></li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><a href=\"https://technote.space/uploads/2019/04/size-setting.png\"><img src=\"https://technote.space/uploads/2019/04/size-setting.png\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"1437\" data-link=\"/y-proofreading/attachment/size-setting\" class=\"wp-image-1437\"></a></figure></li></ul>\n\n<p>右上の三点リーダー⇒『サイズ設定』からサイズ設定を行うことができます。</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"プラグインの再固定\">プラグインの再固定<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#プラグインの再固定\"><svg class=\"icon icon-link\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-labelledby=\"paperclipIconTitle\" stroke=\"#2329EE\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-linejoin=\"miter\" fill=\"none\" color=\"#131996\"><path d=\"M7.93517339,13.7795989 L15.1617306,6.55304173 C16.03921,5.67631227 17.4656766,5.67631227 18.343156,6.55304173 C19.2206355,7.43052116 19.2206355,8.85773771 18.343156,9.73521714 L8.40091248,19.5477137 C6.93619681,21.0124294 4.56325242,21.0124294 3.09853675,19.5477137 C1.63382108,18.083748 1.63382108,15.7093037 3.09853675,14.245338 L12.9335328,4.53783896 C14.9839848,2.48738701 18.3094068,2.48738701 20.3568588,4.53783896 C22.4088107,6.58904088 22.4088107,9.91146301 20.3583588,11.961915 L13.2390491,19.0819746\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https://technote.space/uploads/2019/04/pin-again.png\"><img src=\"https://technote.space/uploads/2019/04/pin-again-177x300.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1439\"></a></figure>\n\n<p>プラグインの固定を外してしまった場合、右上の三点リーダー⇒『再度固定』から再度固定できます。</p>\n\n<h2 id=\"設定\"><a href=\"https://github.com/technote-space/y-proofreading#%E8%A8%AD%E5%AE%9A\"></a>設定<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#設定\"><svg class=\"icon icon-link\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-labelledby=\"paperclipIconTitle\" stroke=\"#2329EE\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-linejoin=\"miter\" fill=\"none\" color=\"#131996\"><path d=\"M7.93517339,13.7795989 L15.1617306,6.55304173 C16.03921,5.67631227 17.4656766,5.67631227 18.343156,6.55304173 C19.2206355,7.43052116 19.2206355,8.85773771 18.343156,9.73521714 L8.40091248,19.5477137 C6.93619681,21.0124294 4.56325242,21.0124294 3.09853675,19.5477137 C1.63382108,18.083748 1.63382108,15.7093037 3.09853675,14.245338 L12.9335328,4.53783896 C14.9839848,2.48738701 18.3094068,2.48738701 20.3568588,4.53783896 C22.4088107,6.58904088 22.4088107,9.91146301 20.3583588,11.961915 L13.2390491,19.0819746\"></path></svg></a></h2>\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/technote-space/y-proofreading/images/assets/screenshot-2.png\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/technote-space/y-proofreading/images/assets/screenshot-2.png\" alt=\"Dashboard\"></a></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"yahooapi-の-client-id\"><a href=\"https://github.com/technote-space/y-proofreading#yahooapi-%E3%81%AE-client-id\"></a>Yahoo!API の Client ID<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#yahooapi-の-client-id\"><svg class=\"icon icon-link\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-labelledby=\"paperclipIconTitle\" stroke=\"#2329EE\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-linecap=\"square\" stroke-linejoin=\"miter\" fill=\"none\" color=\"#131996\"><path d=\"M7.93517339,13.7795989 L15.1617306,6.55304173 C16.03921,5.67631227 17.4656766,5.67631227 18.343156,6.55304173 C19.2206355,7.43052116 19.2206355,8.85773771 18.343156,9.73521714 L8.40091248,19.5477137 C6.93619681,21.0124294 4.56325242,21.0124294 3.09853675,19.5477137 C1.63382108,18.083748 1.63382108,15.7093037 3.09853675,14.245338 L12.9335328,4.53783896 C14.9839848,2.48738701 18.3094068,2.48738701 20.3568588,4.53783896 C22.4088107,6.58904088 22.4088107,9.91146301 20.3583588,11.961915 L13.2390491,19.0819746\"></path></svg></a></h3>\n\n<div class=\"blog-card\"><iframe src=\"https://blog-card-ten.vercel.app/card/https%3A%2F%2Fdeveloper.yahoo.co.jp%2Fyconnect%2Fv2%2Fregistration.html?id=blog-card-m21a5pcbio&#x26;referrer=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnote.space%2Fposts%2Fwpxml-y-proofreading%2F\" frameborder=\"0\" scrolling=\"no\" loading=\"lazy\" data-id=\"blog-card-m21a5pcbio\"></iframe></div>\n\n<p>取得したアプリケーションIDを設定します。<br>アプリケーションの種類は「サーバーサイド」です。<br>シークレットは使用しません。</p>\n\n<h3 id=\"除外する指摘\"><a href=\"https://github.com/technote-space/y-proofreading#%E9%99%A4%E5%A4%96%E3%81%99%E3%82%8B%E6%8C%87%E6%91%98\"></a>除外する指摘<a aria-hidden=\"true\" tabindex=\"-1\" href=\"#除外する指摘\"><svg class=\"icon icon-link\" role=\"img\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" aria-labelledby=\"paperclipIconTitle\" stroke=\"#2329EE\" stroke-width=\"1\" st